        <mxCell id="hp_box" parent="1" style="rounded=1;whiteSpace=wrap;html=1;fillColor=#f5f5f5;strokeColor=#555555;fontSize=12;fontFamily=Helvetica;dashed=1;strokeWidth=2;verticalAlign=middle;" value="&lt;b&gt;Shared Fixed Hyperparameters (all 144 runs)&lt;/b&gt;&lt;br&gt;Backbone: MLP [128, 256, 128] &amp;nbsp;|&amp;nbsp; Activation: GELU &amp;nbsp;|&amp;nbsp; Dropout: 0.2 &amp;nbsp;|&amp;nbsp; Init: Xavier-normal &amp;nbsp;|&amp;nbsp; Batch: 512&lt;br&gt;Optimiser: AdamW (η&lt;sub&gt;0&lt;/sub&gt;=3×10⁻⁴, β&lt;sub&gt;1&lt;/sub&gt;=0.9, β&lt;sub&gt;2&lt;/sub&gt;=0.999, λ&lt;sub&gt;wd&lt;/sub&gt;=0.05) &amp;nbsp;|&amp;nbsp; Schedule: warmup-cosine (e&lt;sub&gt;w&lt;/sub&gt;=5%, r&lt;sub&gt;min&lt;/sub&gt;=10⁻²)&lt;br&gt;Epochs: 3000 &amp;nbsp;|&amp;nbsp; Early stopping patience: 150 &amp;nbsp;|&amp;nbsp; Input noise: σ&lt;sub&gt;n&lt;/sub&gt;=0.02 &amp;nbsp;|&amp;nbsp; Joint weights w=[1, 2.5, 1, 1, 1]&lt;br&gt;Dataset: 66,735 train / 47,868 val / 38,106 test &amp;nbsp;(44 trajectories, 11 Cartesian geometries, 5-DOF Kikobot manipulator)" vertex="1">
